[04:20] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'mean, it\'s it\'s a lot of context to chew off of. So, I think that this makes a very good, uh, example to see exactly, again, how much we can pack in. So, now using our modified prompt along with just our character reference image, uh,'

[04:32] [scene:talk]
