AUDIO: 'at the end. I\'m not sure where that came from. The next logical step was to move past just our character reference and begin moving into storyboard. So, uh, what I actually just ended up doing is taking our modified Coda\'s, uh, prompt there and then, uh, bringing it over to'

[05:17] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'GPT image to just saying, "Hey, uh, make me a storyboard sequence out of this prompt." And this is what it ended up delivering us. So, uh, running this and to note, uh, this is actually going to be a twofer.'

